BSB Bible PDF Toolkit notices
=============================

This is an unofficial community toolkit for building and sharing resources based
on the Berean Standard Bible. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by the
Berean Bible Translation Committee, Bible Hub, Discovery Bible, OpenBible.com,
or the other BSB project partners.

Berean Bible text
-----------------

The Berean Bible and Majority Bible texts were dedicated to the public domain
under CC0 on April 30, 2023. All uses are freely permitted. Attribution is
appreciated but not required.

Official attribution notice from the Berean terms:

The Holy Bible, Berean Standard Bible, BSB is produced in cooperation with Bible
Hub, Discovery Bible, OpenBible.com, and the Berean Bible Translation Committee.
This text of God's Word has been dedicated to the public domain.

Official terms: https://berean.bible/terms.htm

